achus, Pope of Rome]] * [[Symponos]] * [[Synadenos]] * [[Synadene|Synadene, Queen of Hungary]] * [[Syncletica of Alexandria]] * [[Synecdemus]] * [[Synkellos]] * [[Synodianos]] * [[Synodicon Vetus]] * [[Synods of Rome (731)]] * [[Synopsis Chronike (Skoutariotes)]] * [[Syntagma Canonum]] * [[Syracuse, Sicily]] * [[Siege of Syracuse (827–828)|Syracuse, 827–828 Siege of]] * [[Siege of Syracuse (868)|Syracuse, 868 Siege of]] * [[Siege of Syracuse (877–878)|Syracuse, 877–878 Siege of]] * [[Syrgiannes Palaiologos]] * [[Syria (Roman province)]] * [[History of Syria|Syria, History of]] * [[Syriac language]] * [[Syro-Roman law book]]
