{{Orphan|date=January 2015}}
'''Torsten Gregori Aminoff''' (27 August 1910 in [[Tampere]] – 6 October 1985) was a [[Finland|Finnish]] journalist, genealogist and politician. He was a member of the [[Parliament of Finland]] from 1960 to 1962, representing the [[Swedish People's Party of Finland]] (SFP).


